 </svg>OEM Buyer's Bottom Line</h3>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">For consumer charging accessories (phones, laptops, power banks, travel adapters), <strong>GaN V is the clear winner</strong>: lower BOM cost, ultra-compact form factor, and proven supply chain maturity. SiC only makes sense if your product operates continuously above 500W or requires sustained 200C+ thermal tolerance (server PSUs, EV DC fast chargers, industrial motor drives). For the vast majority of OEM charger buyers, GaN delivers the best ROI. Learn more about <a href="https://www.wolfspeed.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brandBlue hover:text-brandOrange">SiC technology at Wolfspeed</a>.</p>
