 </svg>GaN Chip Sourcing</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Major GaN chip suppliers include Navitas, GaN Systems (now acquired by STMicroelectronics), Texas Instruments, and Transphorm. Chinese manufacturers like Innosilicon also offer competitive alternatives. Chip availability can impact lead times — verify supply chain stability before placing large orders.</p>
